---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Academia Europa · European Professional Education Institution"
  description="Structured postgraduate education for experienced professionals. Charcoal-and-bronze institutional home for Veterinary Academy International and future specialist faculties."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="border-b border-divider" style="background-color: var(--color-charcoal-deep);">
    <div class="container-prose py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-6" style="color: var(--color-steel);">European Professional Education</div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-cream text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.02] max-w-5xl">
        Where Professionals<br />Become Authorities.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-cream-dim">
        Academia Europa develops structured postgraduate education for experienced professionals across specialised fields, building the kind of deep, documented mastery that defines genuine clinical and professional authority.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/academies" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Our Academies</a>
        <a href="/partnerships" class="btn">Academic Partnerships</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <Section eyebrow="Our Approach" title="Beyond Fragmented Learning.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-5xl">
      <p>In many professions, continuing education has become fragmented: isolated webinars, disconnected lectures, certificates without progression. Academia Europa was created to offer a more structured path: one that helps experienced professionals build mastery through carefully designed learning architecture, expert instruction, and disciplined academic standards.</p>
      <p>We are not a marketplace of courses. We are a European institution shaping a long-term ecosystem of professional education.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Featured Academy — VAI -->
  <Section eyebrow="First Academy" title="Veterinary Academy International." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>VAI is the veterinary faculty of Academia Europa, dedicated to structured postgraduate education for veterinarians and veterinary teams. Evidence-based, accreditation-aligned, and built for professionals who demand more than fragmented CPD.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="https://vai.vet" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit VAI</a>
      <a href="/academies/vai" class="btn">Learn More</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl italic text-stone text-sm">Further academies in development. Expressions of interest welcome.</p>
  </Section>

  <!-- Light relief — The Academic Framework -->
  <section style="background-color: #F5F0E8; color: #2C2A27;">
    <div class="container-prose py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-5xl">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-5" style="color: #8B6914;">The Academic Framework</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Standards and governance are not a formality here.</h2>
        <div class="rule-gold mt-6" style="background: #8B6914;"></div>
        <p class="mt-10 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #2C2A27;">
          Every programme developed under Academia Europa is built to a documented standard: defined learning objectives, structured module design, evidence-level distinctions, faculty documentation, assessment criteria, and scheduled review cycles. This is not compliance language. It is the foundation of educational integrity.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-14">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color: #8B6914;">Learning Design</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Programmes are structured as complete learning systems, not collections of isolated content.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color: #8B6914;">Evidence Standards</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Content is developed with defined evidence-level distinctions, reflecting the discipline of clinical reasoning.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color: #8B6914;">Review Cycles</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">All programmes undergo scheduled review to maintain currency, accuracy, and professional relevance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-14 text-center">
          <a href="/academic-standards" class="inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.16em] uppercase transition-colors" style="color: #8B6914;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#A07820'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#8B6914'">View Academic Standards →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Academic Standards -->
  <Section eyebrow="Academic Discipline" title="Standards and governance, documented.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-5xl">
      <p>Academia Europa programmes are developed with defined learning objectives, structured modules, faculty documentation, evidence-level distinctions, assessment design, and review cycles. The model supports CPD/CE alignment and external professional review where applicable, with any recognition stated clearly once formally granted.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/academic-standards" class="btn">Academic Standards</a>
        <a href="/academic-governance" class="btn">Governance Framework</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Closing CTA — three audiences -->
  <section style="background-color: var(--color-charcoal-deep);">
    <div class="container-prose py-14 md:py-20">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-cream text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight max-w-4xl">
        Academia Europa welcomes professionals, educators, and institutional partners.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-14 max-w-5xl">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow mb-4">Professionals</div>
          <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Structured programmes designed for practitioners seeking documented progression and genuine mastery.</p>
          <a href="/academies" class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors">Explore Programmes →</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow mb-4">Faculty</div>
          <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Teaching opportunities for specialists committed to rigorous, evidence-informed professional education.</p>
          <a href="/faculty" class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors">Join as Faculty →</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow mb-4">Institutions</div>
          <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Academic review, co-development, and partnership frameworks for aligned professional bodies.</p>
          <a href="/partnerships" class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors">Discuss Partnership →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
